official_title: Unidos Contra El VPH: Screening Preference and Uptake of HPV Self-sampling Among Latinxs Along the US-Mexico Border
inclusion_criteria:
* Individuals with a cervix who are 30-65 years and have not undergone a Pap test in at least three years.
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 30 Years
Must have maximum age of 65 Years
exclusion_criteria: * Having had a hysterectomy or a personal history of cervical cancer.
